explains: v. 估算，计算；<美，非正式>不合情理，讲不通；用计算机计算
wordGroup: beyond compute 不可计量，无法计算；难以估计

sentences.en: At the top of the list is the notion that intelligence is measured by your ability to solve complex problems; to read, write and compute at certain levels; and to resolve abstract equations quickly.
sentences.cn: 最重要的一点是，智力是通过你解决复杂问题的能力来衡量的；一定的读写和计算能力；能快速解出抽象方程。

sentences.en: The Six Sigma Black Belt should be able to compute the mean and standard deviation from a grouped frequency distribution.
sentences.cn: 六西格玛黑带应该能够计算出一个分组发生频次分布数据的均值和标准偏差。
